title: Stash Guys, Sleepers, and the Dark Knights Return | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 299)
description:
The Ringer's Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly spotlight which fantasy sleepers to pick up this week (02:00), intriguing defensive matchups to exploit (19:30), and which wide receivers to stash for later in the season (31:15).
